title: Cobblestone Cyclocross Race
course: Pole Green park is positioned next to Pole Green Elementary School: The course will utilize portions of the park and school land.  Flat open playing field with 2-3 sets of barriers, gravel road sections, a technical off camber swithchback section, fast descents, 20 meter run up, paved bus trunaround, cinder track crossing leading back down a rolling hill to the open fields.  Course lap is 2K and time estimated at 9-13 minutes
